title: PMLN’ candidate Rana Tanvir Hussain wins NA-114 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Rana Tanvir Hussain has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-114, Sheikhupura II by securing 100,039 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent Candidate Arshad Mehmood Chaudhary, who bagged 82,026, votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 51.92 percent.
